text: Ur kwen Ipqassa Oebbi $ef tgallit n tkerkas. Maca, a kwen Iqiss $ef tgallit n uuee. Takweffaot is: a ppecceccem mraw ime$ban, akken tecceccam tawacult nnwen, ne$ a ten tesselsem, ne$ a psereem i wakli. Win ur nwaa ara, ad iueum krav wussan. D tagi ay d takweffaot n tgallit nnwen, ma teggullem. Eiifet di tgallit nnwen. Akka i wen d Ipbeggin Oebbi issekniyen, amar a ppesnemmrem
